# Google AdSense Configuration
#
# After getting approved by Google AdSense, update these values in index.html

# =============================================================================
# STEP 1: Replace Your Publisher ID
# =============================================================================
# Find in index.html (appears 5 times):
#   ca-pub-XXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXX
#
# Replace with your actual Publisher ID from AdSense dashboard
# Example: ca-pub-1234567890123456
#
YOUR_PUBLISHER_ID=ca-pub-XXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXX


# =============================================================================
# STEP 2: Replace Ad Slot IDs
# =============================================================================
# After creating ad units in AdSense, replace these slot IDs:

# Ad Slot 1: Top Banner (Horizontal Display Ad)
TOP_BANNER_SLOT=YYYYYYYYYY

# Ad Slot 2: In-feed Top (Native Ad before content)
INFEED_TOP_SLOT=YYYYYYYYYY

# Ad Slot 3: In-feed Bottom (Native Ad after content)
INFEED_BOTTOM_SLOT=YYYYYYYYYY

# Ad Slot 4: Sidebar (Vertical Display Ad - Desktop only)
SIDEBAR_SLOT=YYYYYYYYYY


# =============================================================================
# HOW TO FIND THESE VALUES
# =============================================================================
# 1. Login to https://www.google.com/adsense
# 2. Publisher ID: Account → Account Information
# 3. Ad Slot IDs: Ads → By ad unit → Create ad units
#
# For detailed instructions, see ADSENSE_SETUP.md


# =============================================================================
# SEARCH & REPLACE GUIDE
# =============================================================================
# Use your code editor's Find & Replace feature:
#
# Find:    ca-pub-XXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXX
# Replace: ca-pub-YOUR_ACTUAL_ID
#
# Then replace each YYYYYYYYYY with the corresponding slot ID


# =============================================================================
# VERIFICATION
# =============================================================================
# After updating:
# 1. Save index.html
# 2. Deploy your website
# 3. Check AdSense dashboard (may take 24-48 hours to show data)
# 4. Use browser DevTools to verify ads are loading
#
# Tip: Open Console (F12) and look for AdSense errors


# =============================================================================
# IMPORTANT NOTES
# =============================================================================
# - Keep your Publisher ID confidential (don't commit to public repos)
# - Don't click your own ads (violates AdSense policy)
# - Allow 24-48 hours for ads to start showing
# - Ensure your site is publicly accessible
# - Check that ads.txt file is configured (if required)
